      "writtenOn": "2019-02-04T18:10:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "that\u0027s assuming (1) the var isn\u0027t already set in the existing env and (2) the child code is working correctly.  if (2) is broken, and you do `export TEST_VAR\u003dtest` before running the unittests, then the unittest isn\u0027t going to detect that right ?",
